What is OSPF?

IGP Routing Protocol
used inside an autonomous system

Link-State Algorithm
every router knows the network topology

Shortest Path First selection
Dijkstra algorithm

auto discovery of routers

Open Standard (RFC 2740)
vs. proprietary protocols like Cizzzcoeee EIGRP
driven by an IETF committee

